#: src/menus/view/display-filters.xml:409(term)
msgid "Show bogus"
msgstr "Mostra falso"

#: src/menus/view/display-filters.xml:411(para)
msgid ""
"Enable visualization for not-a-number (NaN) pixels, only visible when there "
